HEADWORD: machine-like
<hw>machine-like</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<def>behaving in an unthinking manner, like the functioning of a
machine; <as>as, <ex>machine-like</ex> fools</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> automatic, automaton-like, automatonlike,
machinelike, robotlike.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

